ntro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":null,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":null,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":null,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"0\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', '13', '0', '1', '', '', '1', '47', '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', '0', '*', ''), ('84', '194', 'About Us', 'about-us', '', '<div class=\"twothirds\">\r\n<p>KB Murals produces premium tile mural products for commercial and residential spaces. Our beautiful tile murals are easy to install and create a dramatic effect in any space.</p>\r\n<p class=\"titletxt\">What KB Murals Can Do For You</p>\r\n<p><strong>Residential Buyers. </strong> KB Murals makes transforming your wall décor easy. Tile murals used to be considered an expensive home upgrade, but KB has combined the best selection and installation process to save you hundreds! Our products are a simple, affordable way to increase your home’s value, indulge the interior designer within you, and bring your home to life.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Commercial Buyers. </strong> KB Murals is transforming commercial spaces with beautiful custom tile murals. Our Custom tile murals allow you to create small to large-scale applications. The lightweight tiles make installation simple and inexpensive compared to other products.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Interior Designers. </strong> KB Murals is a leader in design and luxury decor. The scenic vistas and custom themes provide inspired looks and relaxing escapes from the home or office. KB Murals also offers complete themed collections for kitchens and baths. You can match tile murals to coasters, cutting boards, mats, plates and more! Our products are a simple, affordable way to decorate and design interior spaces.</p>\r\n<p class=\"titletxt\">Our Products</p>\r\n<p>KB Murals offers two types of tile murals: Ready to Hang Tile Murals and Custom Tile Murals. We also offer customization within those categories for tile materials, frames, images, coating, and size.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Ready to Hang Murals. </strong> KB Murals is the first company to offer tile murals complete with tile, frame and backing. Other tile mural companies create the individual tiles, and then leave the customer to figure out how to install the mural into your existing tile. At KB Murals, we take away that confusing task.</p>\r\n<p>We are the first company to design all parts of the tile mural display – the tile itself, the frame, backing, and adhesive. This benefits you in two ways: first you avoid the headache of having to learn about proper tile installation; second, and more importantly, you receive a beautifully matched frame that enhances the aesthetic appeal of your mural.</p>\r\n<p>Our Ready to Hang Murals includes everything you need to install it yourself as well as easy-to-follow instructions. Our murals are applied directly on top of your existing tiles, no there is no need to hire an expensive contractor or remove your existing tiles.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Custom Tile Murals. </strong> We also offer Custom tile murals that can be installed into an existing backsplash, bathroom tile, and more. KB Murals can produce a wide range of mural sizes with options to customize dimensions, images, materials and more. KB Murals also offers customization on our Ready to Hang Tile Murals. This way, you can use your desired image, and still receive the complete installation package including: tiles, frame, backing, and adhesive.</p>\r\n<p>KB Murals provides the complete solution to installing backsplashes and bathroom wall tile. Shop for everything you’ll need to upgrade your home today. Our affordable prices and ready to hang pieces will provide you with everything you need to install the tile mural yourself.</p>\r\n<div class=\"clear\"> </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"onethird\">\r\n<div class=\"link\">\r\n<h3>Ready to Hang Murals</h3>\r\n<div id=\"video_ready_hang\"> </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"link\">\r\n<h3>Creat your own Murals</h3>\r\n<div id=\"video_customize\"> </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', '1', '0', '0', '81', '2012-10-19 23:17:29', '475', '', '2013-03-12 19:07:46', '475', '0', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-10-19 23:17:29', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":null,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":null,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":null,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"0\",\"link_category\":\"0\",\"show_parent_category\":\"0\",\"link_parent_category\":\"0\",\"show_author\":\"0\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', '25', '0', '1', '', '', '1', '194', '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', '0', '*', ''), ('85', '195', 'Our Process', 'ourprocess', '', '<div class=\"twothirds\">\r\n<p>KB Murals’ products are created with the best materials, production methods, and shipment and installation processes. There are four main parts to producing a tile mural: Design, production, shipping, and installation.</p>\r\n<p class=\"titletxt\">Design</p>\r\n<p>The first step to creating a tile mural is the design phase. In this phase, you can choose from one of our designs or upload your own image. KB Murals carries hundreds of popular tile mural paintings, photographs, images, and more. From traditional to contemporary, we have a style for everyone.</p>\r\n<p>The design phase also allows you to select the mural size, tile size, materials, coating, frame, and more. You can also choose between permanent and removable tile mural options. The Ready to Hang Murals can either be applied directly to the tile using adhesive, or comes complete with removable hook and hanger.</p>\r\n<p>Once you’ve designed your mural to preference, your specifications are then sent to the art department to begin production.</p>\r\n<p class=\"titletxt\">Production</p>\r\n<p>KB Murals’ streamlined production process creates beautiful, vivid tile murals using the most innovative techniques in the industry. The production phase is divided into three main parts:</p>\r\n<ol><ol>\r\n<li>The art department use sublimation dyes to print your image onto heat transfer paper</li>\r\n<li>The printed picture is then set on top of the tile mural and placed into a convection oven</li>\r\n<li>The image is then transferred onto the tile using a process called dye sublimation.</li>\r\n</ol></ol>\r\n<p>Please see our Sublimation Dye Guide for more information on the dye sublimation process.</p>\r\n<p class=\"titletxt\">Shipping</p>\r\n<p>KB Murals ensures secure delivery for each and every mural. The tiles are first wrapped and then placed carefully into a boxed package. The tile murals are generally produced and shipped within 4 to 6 business days, depending on the size of the mural.</p>\r\n<p class=\"titletxt\">Installation</p>\r\n<p>KB Murals’ Ready to Hang Murals require no invasive installation processes. To install the tile mural, simply remove the adhesive backing and place the mural level against the desired location. The super-strong adhesive will hold the mural permanently in place on top of the tile. To learn more about installing your permanent Ready to Hang Mural, please click here.</p>\r\n<p>For renters and individuals who prefer the ability to move their mural, we also offer a removable option for our Ready to Hang Murals. The removable murals are attached to the wall using a hook and nail system (similar to a traditional photo frame). This will allow you to hang and remove your mural as needed. To learn more about installing your removable Ready to Hang Mural, please click here.</p>\r\n<p>KB Murals also offers custom tile murals that can be installed into your backsplash, bathroom tile, and more. Custom tile murals can be installed into the existing tile using traditional installation techniques. Some customers prefer this process because it allows them to create a more fluid effect between the mural and surrounding tile. To learn more about tile installation, please click here.</p>\r\n<p class=\"titletxt\">Get Your Tile Mural Today</p>\r\n<p>Increasing your home’s value is just a few clicks away! Our tile murals are built to last and come with a satisfaction guarantee. Not only are they an affordable alternative to traditional renovations, they also enhance any space with their eye-catching design. For more information regarding our process or products, please contact our Customer Service team. We are happy to answer any questions you have!</p>\r\n</div>', '', '1', '0', '0', '81', '2012-10-19 23:20:40', '475', '', '2013-03-12 19:13:16', '475', '0', '0000-00-00 00