nformation. By using this website, you consent to the collection and use of your information as outlined in this document. In the circumstance that we update the content of this policy, we will notify you via email or by placing a notice on our website. We encourage you to review this policy regularly. Your continued use of the KB Murals website will be subject to the then current privacy policy.</p>\r\n<p class=\"titletxt\">Uploading and Posting Information</p>\r\n<p>When you register for an account, you will provide us with a username and password. When you post a review on the site, your username is visible to the public. Any content that you upload to the site is not considered personally identifiable information subject to this Privacy Policy.</p>\r\n<p class=\"titletxt\">Personal Information</p>\r\n<p>You may provide us with personal information when you:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Register for a KB Murals account;</li>\r\n<li>Purchase a product or use our services;</li>\r\n<li>Sign up for newsletters, email alerts and special offers.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Such information may include, but is not limited to, your name, email address, billing address, shipping address, and credit card number.</p>\r\n<p class=\"titletxt\">Cookies</p>\r\n<p>KB Murals uses cookies on its website. A cookie is a small piece of data sent from a website and stored in a user’s web browser while a user is browsing a website. Cookies do not store personally identifiable information.</p>\r\n<p class=\"titletxt\">Securing Your Information</p>\r\n<p>When you place an order or access your account information, we use a safeguard to secure your information. The secure server software (SSL) we use encrypts all information you input before it is sent to us. In addition, your account information is password protected for your privacy and security.</p>\r\n<p class=\"titletxt\">Using Your Information</p>\r\n<p>We use your information to process orders and to communicate with you about the status of your order and other inquiries about our products and services. We may also use your email address to send marketing messages and notifications. You may unsubscribe to the notifications at any time.</p>\r\n<p class=\"titletxt\">Changing, Deleting, or Updating Your Information</p>\r\n<p>Most of your account information will be stored in the KB Murals database. If you have questions about what information is stored or would like to obtain a copy of such information, please contact us at.</p>\r\n<p>After receiving proof of your identity, we will provide the information to you and delete or change any information requested.</p>\r\n<p>This current version of the KB Murals Privacy Policy was adopted effective 03/12/2013.</p>\r\n</div>', '', '1', '0', '0', '84', '2012-10-22 00:19:29', '475', '', '2013-03-12 19:32:37', '475', '0', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-10-22 00:19:29', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":null,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":null,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":null,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', '22', '0', '3', '', '', '1', '53', '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\