mily pictures to scenic vistas, a custom tile mural is sure to enhance your home. This brief guide will explain which image files to use to achieve the best possible print.</p>\r\n<p class=\"titletxt\">Image Formats</p>\r\n<p>Creating a tile mural is made easy with KB Murals. Simply click the “upload image” button to browse computer files and select an image. We accept the following image formats:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>JPEG web image (.jpg/.jpeg)</li>\r\n<li>GIF web image (.gif)</li>\r\n<li>Bitmap image (.bpm)</li>\r\n<li>PNG image (.png)</li>\r\n<li>Postscript file (.ps)</li>\r\n<li>Tagged image (.tiff/.tif)</li>\r\n<li>EPS vector image (.eps)</li>\r\n<li>Photoshop doc (.psd)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"titletxt\">Image Size</p>\r\n<p>As a general rule of thumb, choose a high-resolution image to produce an excellent print. Pictures shot with an eight mega pixel camera or higher are preferred. The appropriate image size will depend on the size and dimensions of the mural.</p>\r\n<p>Custom tile murals require the image to be large enough to product a high-quality print. For questions regarding image size, resolution, and quality please contact our Customer Service team.</p>\r\n<p class=\"titletxt\">Copyright Guidelines</p>\r\n<p>KB Murals will not print copyrighted images without written permission from the copyright owner. We reserve the right to reject any image at our sole discretion. If your image is found to be unsuitable in any way, your credit card will be refunded in full.</p>\r\n<p class=\"titletxt\">Stock Photography Sites</p>\r\n<p>If you can’t find what you’re looking for on our site, nor do you have a picture readily available to customize your mural, KB Murals recommends purchasing a stock image from 123rf.com, thinkstock.com, or istockphoto.com. These sites will grant you permission from the copyright owner to use their image. For further image quality questions, please contact our Customer Service. Our team is happy to help!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"onethird\">\r\n<div class=\"link\">\r\n<h3>Ready to Hang Murals</h3>\r\n<div id=\"video_ready_hang\"> </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"link\">\r\n<h3>Creat your own Murals</h3>\r\n<div id=\"video_customize\"> </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', '1', '0', '0', '89', '2012-10-24 19:49:18', '475', '', '2013-03-12 19:06:27', '475', '0', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-10-24 19:49:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":null,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":null,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":null,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', '6', '0', '0', '', '', '1', '20', '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', '0', '*', '');
